RT @NYDailyNews: A 32-year-old boxer was fatally shot on a return visit home to Staten Island early Sunday.

Grashino Yancy, a 2019 Daily News Golden Gloves competitor, was struck in the right leg on Park Hill Ave. near Palma Drive in Park Hill about 12:45 a.m., cops said.
